,"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event17-02-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"덧없고…… 덧없……\n이런, 츠구미 짱이지 않은가. 대체 무슨 일이니?\n설마하니 날 만나러 와준 거려나?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"kime05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"event17-02-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"네, 네! 맞아요!\n저, 실은……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event17-02-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"후후…… 솔직한 아기 고양이구나.\n어쩜 이리도 사랑스러운지.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"event17-02-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"아, 아기 고양이!? 저기…… 연극부가 문화제에서 하는\n공연에 대해서 질문이 있는데요……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event17-02-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"아아, 뭘까?\n무엇이든 물어봐도 괜찮아.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"event17-02-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"어제 연극부에서 제출한 신청 서류를\n확인해봤는데요…… 줄리엣 역할로 치사토 씨의 이름이\n있어서 그게 사실인지 여쭤보려고……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event17-02-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"그럼, 정말이고 말고.\n줄리엣 역할은 치사토야.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"event17-02-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"여, 역시 정말이었구나……!\n교장 선생님께 허가는 받으신 건가요?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event17-02-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"아니, 아직이지.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"event17-02-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"네~~~~~~엣!?\n무, 문화제까지 이제 한 달밖에 남지 않았다고요!?\n괜찮은 건가요!?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event17-02-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"걱정마렴. 셰익스피어는 이렇게 말했지.\n「가파른 언덕을 오르기 위해서는 먼저 천천히 걷는 것이\n필요하다.」라고. 즉…… 그런 거다.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"event17-02-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"즈, 즉……? 으아아, 어쩌지……!\n나 혼자서는 세타 선배랑 도무지 말이 안 통할 것 같아~!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"odoodo01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event17-02-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"어라? 하자와 씨 아니십니까~\n카오루 씨랑 대체 무엇을 하고 계신겁니까?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event17-02-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"아앗! 마야 선배~!\n살았다……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"awate01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event17-02-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"왜 그러십니까? 울 것 같은 표정이지 말입니다.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event17-02-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"과연~ 문화제의 이야기였습니까!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event17-02-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"네. 치사토 씨의 이름이 있어서, 정말인지 세타 선배한테\n물어보려고 왔는데요……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event17-02-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"그, 그게…… 세타 선배 월드가 굉장해서……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"odoodo01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event17-02-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"후후…… 다시금 난 죄 없는 아기 고양이를 홀리고 만 모양이구나.\n미안하구나. 츠구미 짱.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"kime02","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"event17-02-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"아하하. 카오루 씨는 확실히 재밌는 분이시지 말입니다.\n그에 대한 사정은 제가 설명하겠습니다.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event17-02-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"올해는 연극부 창립 10주년을 기념하는 해입니다.\n그렇다 보니 올해 공연은\n평소보다 특별한 것을 하고 싶다고 생각해서……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event17-02-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"그래서 게스트를 모시는게 어떨까\n했습니다! 새로운 분이 한 분 오시는 것만으로도\n부원들한테는 엄청난 자극이 되기도 하니 말입니다.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event17-02-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"그래서 내가 치사토는 어떠하냐고 제안을 한 것이란다.\n내가 했지만 완벽한 제안이지 싶구나.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"event17-02-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"치사토는 내 오랜 친구니까 말이지.\n분명 우리 두 사람의 연기 상성도 발군이겠지.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"kime01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"event17-02-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"게스트로, 그것도 치사토 씨를 모신다면 \n부원들의 사기도 올라갈 것이고 결과적으로 퀄리티 높은 무대를\n만들 수 있지 않을까 싶었습니다.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event17-02-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"……그렇기 때문에 이번 일에는 연극부의 뜻이 담겨 있습니다.\n절대 카오루 씨 혼자만의 생각이 아닙니다.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event17-02-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"그렇게 된 거로군요.\n아아, 하지만! 시간이 없다는 건 변하지 않아요!\n교장 선생님의 허가도 필요하고……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event17-02-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"치사토 씨가 오신다면 문화제 날 체육관 인력도\n늘려야 하고……!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event17-02-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"이례적인 일이니 사전에 학생회 분들과\n상담을 하는 게 좋았을 걸 그랬습니다…… 죄송합니다!\n최대한 학생회에는 민폐를 끼치지 않도록 하겠습니다!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event17-02-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"아뇨! 기념 공연인 데다 연극부는 항상 대인기니까요!\n서포트하는 것이 학생회의 역할이에요!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event17-02-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"츠구미 짱…… 그대는 어쩜 이리 갸륵한가……!\n아아! 덧없다……!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"event17-02-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"여, 여튼! 이번 건은 학생회에도 공유해놓을게요!\n도와드릴 게 있다면 뭐든지 할 테니까요!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"awate01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event17-02-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"네! 감사합니다!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event17-02-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"그럼 전 바로 학생회에 이번 건에 대해 이야기하고 올게요!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event17-02-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"하자와 씨는 카오루 씨가 말씀하신 것처럼 정말 노력가면서\n멋진 분이십니다~ 저희도 열심히 해야겠습니다!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event17-02-038","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"아아, 그렇구나. 아기 고양이가 슬퍼할 만한 일은\n하고 싶지 않구나. 한 번 더 치사토한테 전화를 해봐야겠군.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"event17-02-039","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDi